-- Santos Wins Madeira Islands Open for First European Tour Title
-- B y   J a m e s   C o n e
-- 2012-05-13T14:18:33Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-05-13/santos-wins-madeira-islands-open-for-first-european-tour-title.html
Portugal ’s Ricardo Santos shot a 9-
under-par final-round today to win golf’s Madeira Islands Open
for a first title on the European Tour.  Santos finished on 22-under, four shots ahead of Sweden’s
Magnus Carlsson, with Andreas Harto of Denmark another shot
back.  Santos collects a check for 112,500 euros ($145,300), the
biggest of the 29-year-old’s career.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
James Cone at 
 jcone@bloomberg.net  